@Lain: It's already *technically* usable. It's pretty slow though, and lacks a lot of features I want to put in it. Right now it's a streamer/downloader for two popular chinese music sites: Xiami and Netease Music. Here's some screenshots:

[artist page](https://ipfs.pics/ipfs/QmWDSYSh2cEzUpnyLD4cPSWHcrVbNyg398JgbySeirb72x) - Grabs all the albums available, along with last.fm and musicbrainz data. Similar artists shown at the top there.

