[Album page+playing queued songs](https://ipfs.pics/ipfs/QmaicZJuVkMJgqQEZseVJY8uVp7kjKutqeUqMiQNrtSSF4) - Shows the tracks from both services, along with a variety of play/queue/download buttons. Has options to directly download a track or to download the whole album. The app automatically tags mp3s, and sorts into `artist/album/track.mp3`. Lyrics are obtained if available.

